1. On je postavio cilj* da obrazuje svoju porodicu. (He set a goal to provide for his family.)

2. Ona je postigla svoj cilj* da postane uspešna. (She achieved her goal to become successful.)

3. Povezivanje sa ljudima je bio njegov cilj*. (Connecting with people was his goal.)

4. Njihov cilj* je da postanu najbolji. (Their goal is to become the best.)

5. Ona je postigla svoj cilj* da završi studije. (She achieved her goal to finish her studies.)

6. On je postavio cilj* da postane dobar učitelj. (He set a goal to become a good teacher.)